data.description: Huge price reduction!   Looking for a cozy retreat in Stone Mountain? Look no further than 972 Lake Watch Drive! This split-level home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, waiting for your personal touch. While cosmetic repairs are needed, worry not- the HVAC system was upgraded in 2019. Don't miss this opportunity to transform this house into your dream home. (HOME INSPECTION WAS COMPLETED ON 12/27/2023, request it and we will give it to you for free!) Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home. Schedule a showing today! This property is being sold "as is." Prospective buyers are encouraged to perform all necessary inspections and evaluations prior to purchase. House is not vacant!!! Do not use ShowingTime, Agent is ONLY transactional do not reach out to him, our info is in private remarks, Check out the really good 3D Matterport virtual tour! It shows you everything! Property Problem Solvers will help you solve your problem, for more details get in touch with us!
